P = sum((murder[,20] == 3))
N = nrow(murder) - P
TP = sum(murder[,39] >= 0.4 & murder[,20] == 3)
TN = sum(murder[,39] < 0.4 & murder[,20] == 2)
FN = sum(murder[,39] < 0.4 & murder[,20] == 3)
FP = sum(murder[,39] >= 0.4 & murder[,20] == 2)
ACC = (TP + TN) / (P + N)
FPR = 1 - TN / N
TPR = TP / P
